OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will stay
OL,6,Fcloudy through the evening and
OL,7,Fovernight with outbreaks of rain or
OL,8,Fdrizzle, heavy at times. Perhaps drier
OL,9,Ffor a time around midnight.
OL,10,
OL,11,CThursday:FCloud and rain at first,
OL,12,Fclearing northeast in the morning to
OL,13,Fallow some bright spells. A band of
OL,14,Frain will pass through in the
OL,15,Fafternoon, followed by showers.
OL,16,FOccasionally windy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
