OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FBright
OL,6,Fwith showers on Friday, windy at
OL,7,Ffirst. Drier with bright spells on
OL,8,FSaturday. Windier again on Sunday with
OL,9,Fvariable cloud with some outbreaks of
OL,10,Frain.
